ores-temporales" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">Marcadores temporales</a></li></ul><h4 class="font-semibold">Imperfecto</h4><ul class="list-disc list-inside text-purple-700"><li><a href="https://sites.google.com/view/srscalici/apuntes/verbos/imperfecto/" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">Notas generales</a></li><li><a href="https://sites.google.com/view/srscalici/apuntes/verbos/imperfecto/1" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">Conjugaciones</a></li></ul>
  
